<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_89_r2l3"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Als vns ewr gnad <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von des <expan>Pfarr<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒü Hawſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r2l4">darvmb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir den Jacob Topler <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü rede geſacʒt / . vnd der ſprichet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r2l5">Er wöll <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eıgentlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . wie es vmb <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r2l6"><expan>gelege<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeÿ / . vnd vvo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb vnd dıenſt <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> / des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_89_r2l7"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvır vvıllıg vnd <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> <expan>vj̃</expan> . <expan>An<ex>te</ex></expan> Letare / x<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / </ab>
