<ab>Byschof czü <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als uns ewr gnad
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von des
                            <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> czü Hawsen, darumb
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den Jacob Topler,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, czü rede gesaczt und der sprichet, er wöll
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eigentlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie es umb
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache
                            <expan>gelege<ex>n</ex></expan> sey. Und wo wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und dienst
                            <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wir willig
                        und <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>vi</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> letare x<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
